  "detailed_description": "「In 1946, a full-scale counteroffensive operation was launched against the Japanese army, which has vast Pacific Ocean areas.<br>Shoot the enemy fleet, break in the iron-clad Pacific defense line and Show the American spirit.」<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564690/extras/b4b18e938dadaa9806e68868b67acc35.avif?t=1627746606\" width=700 height=392 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This Game Is A top-down 2d Shooter</h2><br>Features<br><br>Simple gameplay that follows the good old 2D shooting game system<br>Three types of aircraft can be selected<br>Each has features such as wide range type, centralized type, and high power type.<br>Your ship is usually with a shot In addition, it has an emergency bomb and a support aircraft attack,<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564690/extras/4d54ef78dcde36b484b69919df8d6652.avif?t=1627746606\" width=480 height=328 /></span><br>Support aircraft attacks can be participated in the attack by using the Charge gauge.<br>Support machines are also characterized by wide-range type, centralized type, and high-power type.<br>By combining it with your own attack, you can make more efficient attacks.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564690/extras/3563a75c07d016d7f7bdb7b8d1596240.avif?t=1627746606\" width=512 height=1080 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564690/extras/bfa01248e07b90127533be85280d5379.avif?t=1627746606\" width=512 height=1080 /></span><br>Controller&Keyboard Settings<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1564690/extras/23ca3007338216a6568132887dc49fb6.avif?t=1627746606\" width=600 height=392 /></span>",
